<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Silhouette Lores • Collaborations</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
  <style>
    .collab-highlight {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1e1e, #2a2a2a);
      border: 1px solid #444;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .collab-highlight h2 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .collab-highlight p {
      color: #ccc;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .collab-email {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .collab-email a {
      color: #ffb347;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .collab-email a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="site-header">
  <div class="header-flex">
    <img src="Logo_v4.png" alt="Silhouette Lores Logo" class="site-logo-block" draggable="false" />

    <div class="header-text">
      <h1 class="site-title">Silhouette Lores</h1>

      <p>
          Join Us:
          <a href="#" target="_blank" class="link">Instagram</a> |
          <a href="#" target="_blank" class="link">Facebook</a> |
          <a href="#" target="_blank" class="link">YouTube</a> |
          <a href="mailto:bineet.photography@gmail.com" class="link">Email</a>
      </p>

      <p>Love what you see? Reach out to make it yours.</p>
	  <p><b>Want your business featured across Facebook, Instagram, YouTube & our Website? Let’s collaborate.</b></p>
      <p>All photos & contents &copy; Bineet Ghosh. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p><i><b>I post emotions, not autobiography</b></i></p>

      <nav class="top-menu">
        <a href="index.html" class="nav-link">Home</a>
        <a href="archive.html" target="_blank" class="nav-link">Archive</a>
        <a href="calm.html" class="nav-link">Calm & Comfort</a>
        <a href="series.html" class="nav-link">Education & Series</a>
        <a href="collaborations.html" class="nav-link">Collaborations</a>
		<a href="free.html" class="nav-link">Free Downloads</a>
      </nav>

    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="collab-highlight">
  <h2>Collaborate With Us</h2>
  <p>
    At Silhouette Lores, we don’t just create content — we tell stories that people feel.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you are a brand, hotel, café, creator, or business looking to showcase your space, experience, or story,
    we would love to collaborate with you.
  </p>
  <p>
    Through cinematic visuals, emotional storytelling, and a strong presence across Instagram, Facebook, YouTube, and our website,
    we help your brand connect with people in a way that feels authentic and memorable.
  </p>
  <p>
    From travel stays and local businesses to unique experiences and creative ideas — if your story deserves to be told, we’re here to tell it.
  </p>
  <p class="collab-email">
    📩 Reach out: <a href="mailto:bineet.photography@gmail.com">bineet.photography@gmail.com</a>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="gallery">

  <div class="photo-card">
    <div class="image-container">
      <img src="Logo_v4.png" alt="Collaboration 1" />
      <div class="watermark">© Silhouette Lores</div>
    </div>
    <div class="photo-info">
      <h3>Partner Business One</h3>
      <p>A beautiful collaboration highlighting their space, story, and experience.</p>
      <p>
        🔗 <a href="#" target="_blank" class="archive-link">Visit</a><br>
        ▶️ <a href="#" target="_blank" class="archive-link">Watch Feature</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="photo-card">
    <div class="image-container">
      <img src="Logo_v4.png" alt="Collaboration 2" />
      <div class="watermark">© Silhouette Lores</div>
    </div>
    <div class="photo-info">
      <h3>Partner Business Two</h3>
      <p>Capturing the essence of their brand through storytelling and visuals.</p>
      <p>
        🔗 <a href="#" target="_blank" class="archive-link">Visit</a><br>
        ▶️ <a href="#" target="_blank" class="archive-link">Watch Feature</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="photo-card">
    <div class="image-container">
      <img src="Logo_v4.png" alt="Collaboration 3" />
      <div class="watermark">© Silhouette Lores</div>
    </div>
    <div class="photo-info">
      <h3>Partner Business Three</h3>
      <p>Showcasing their journey through curated visuals and narrative.</p>
      <p>
        🔗 <a href="#" target="_blank" class="archive-link">Visit</a><br>
        ▶️ <a href="#" target="_blank" class="archive-link">Watch Feature</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>


</section>

<footer>
  <p>
    Find us on
    <a href="#" target="_blank">Instagram</a> ·
    <a href="#" target="_blank">Facebook</a> ·
    <a href="#" target="_blank">YouTube</a>
  </p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
